------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- ◯ commutes with Erased

-- ◯ (Erased A) is equivalent to Erased (◯ A).

◯-Erased≃Erased-◯ : ◯ (Erased A) ≃ Erased (◯ A)
◯-Erased≃Erased-◯ = Eq.⟨ _ , commutes-with-Erased ⟩

